{"tid":1789044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普有機會俾人暗殺/辭退","createTime":"2019-12-19T07:21:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T07:41:28.000Z","uid":150079,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d8fefc840403755baf47eec82e87be26d6c47b8e","tid":1789044,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:21:06.000Z","msg":"對，這張「適可而止」上面印的正是剛剛當選為美國總統的唐納德&middot;川普。卡面上的畫就是川普怒吼的臉，三角形則象徵著金字塔，在共濟會里就是權利的符號。卡牌上的描述則是：「任何時間，任何地點，我們的狙擊手都會放倒你。過得愉快。」很明顯，這是對當時川普的一句威脅，川普已經被曝出並不是共濟會的成員，而誰都不會想到，它現在已經成為了美國的總統。請注意，在上面我都用了過去式，因為以上我們看到的這些卡牌都已是21年前，1995年發行的了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T6zsHVw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT6zsHVw.jpg&h=4f8878ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2523251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2523251&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfAKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=4c361288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2523251</a>"},{"pid":"184c9d42e925348fd52a6d0026285c1605d630c2","tid":1789044,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:22:12.000Z","msg":"奇怪"},{"pid":"749eae318adeabda6687b7ca787bdf87703e2f90","tid":1789044,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:26:05.000Z","msg":"21年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef9e0bec4aa882884413f3ed06b3d6becf43dcba","tid":1789044,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"749eae318adeabda6687b7ca787bdf87703e2f90","tid":1789044,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:26:05.000Z","msg":"21年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:31:22.000Z","msg":"恐怖不"},{"pid":"26b135f510bc9ec05d4d9f0637f17aba26f3d46c","tid":1789044,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"